{"tid":1961892,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【耶撚】 點睇聖經話「男人是女人的頭」","createTime":"2020-04-07T05:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T08:49:47.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb15292f21df5e6007a4d49818ef4ed09b5b52c0","tid":1961892,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"聖經歧視女性？女人無才便是德？<br />\n<br />\n女人本身係比男人弱？<br />\n<br />\n定係女人其實本身比男人強，更有智慧和聰明，但因為人類犯了罪，有暴力和貪婪的風險，所以古時要男人做頭，壓抑女人，令女人無法發揮所長，從而令人類科學與科技發展進步緩慢，從而減少人類滅亡或世界大戰危機？（女權開始左，科學發展快，人類很快就成功研發原子彈，1961年的沙皇炸彈更比1945年原子彈勁千倍。而今日戰爭風險仍未解除。）"},{"pid":"205dda018d7a19cc94dae62e80cc7d99597a643d","tid":1961892,"uid":223428,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"不同角色。<br />\n神創造女仔係男仔嘅幫手，其實係平等嘅，角色唔同啫。"},{"pid":"d723ef3f3d884ce7a26eb1e161b57b247cb6776b","tid":1961892,"uid":223428,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"原子彈係男士發明的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471eda288edc37e8a5a6940c2dbd4e748c4a033a","tid":1961892,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b1ec175b2665c2559c4cb8e51e0e2b9777b34bb","tid":1961892,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"471eda288edc37e8a5a6940c2dbd4e748c4a033a","tid":1961892,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"205dda018d7a19cc94dae62e80cc7d99597a643d","tid":1961892,"uid":223428,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"不同角色。<br />\n神創造女仔係男仔嘅幫手，其實係平等嘅，角色唔同啫。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"收啦，男不是無女，女不是無男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba2409a783d51d12488e9bc16b946d21e55f630","tid":1961892,"uid":339272,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":